      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that a few moments ago, the police fired tear gas at a group of people who were protesting on the way to the Parliament.",
        "It is reported that nearly 5,000 people are currently blocking several roads leading to the Parliament and despite the tear gas attack, those people are still waiting."
